#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn37.5"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn37.5:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 37 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 37 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn37.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamapeyyālavagga "
msgstr "1. Abbreviated Texts "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn37.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Kodhanasutta "
msgstr "5. Irritable "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn37.5:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā anuruddho yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā anuruddho bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Anuruddha went up to the Buddha, sat down to one side, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn37.5:1.2"
msgid "“idhāhaṃ, bhante, mātugāmaṃ passāmi dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjantaṃ. "
msgstr "“Sometimes, sir, with my clairvoyance that’s purified and superhuman, I see that a female—when her body breaks up, after death—is reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell. "

msgctxt "sn37.5:1.3"
msgid "Katīhi nu kho, bhante, dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjatī”ti? "
msgstr "How many qualities do females have so that they’re reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.241, sc2
msgctxt "sn37.5:2.1"
msgid "“Pañcahi kho, anuruddha, dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati. "
msgstr "“Anuruddha, when females have five qualities, when their body breaks up, after death, they are reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell. "

msgctxt "sn37.5:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn37.5:2.3"
msgid "Assaddho ca hoti, ahiriko ca hoti, anottappī ca hoti, kodhano ca hoti, duppañño ca hoti—"
msgstr "They’re faithless, shameless, imprudent, irritable, and witless. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn37.5:2.4"
msgid "imehi kho, anuruddha, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjatī”ti. "
msgstr "When females have these five qualities, when their body breaks up, after death, they are reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn37.5:2.5"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

